{"root":{"data":{"text":"Godot 游戏架构设计实战指南"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"一、理解 Godot 哲学"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"核心原则：拥抱面向对象与组合，不强行引入陌生风格"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"五大基石"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"场景 Scene：组织与复用的基本单元（类似Prefab）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"节点 Node：构成场景的基本功能元素"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"场景树 Scene Tree：运行时结构，游戏循环入口"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"信号 Signal：内建事件系统，解耦通信的核心"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"组合与继承：场景可组合，也可扩展"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"关键启示：用 Godot 的方式思考，而非强行移植其他引擎模式"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"二、精通核心模式（Godot 实现）","layout_fish-bone-master_offset":{"x":284,"y":55}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"游戏循环"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"实现：_process(delta) / _physics_process(delta)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"要点：Engine.time_scale 全局慢动作；区分逻辑与物理更新"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"组件模式"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"实现：场景实例化添加功能子节点（组合优于继承）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"要点：设计独立、松耦合的功能场景"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"ECS 架构"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"实现：GECS (轻量级) / Godot-Bevy (深度集成)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"要点：非原生范式，海量实体管理才建议引入"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"事件系统"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"实现：内置信号 signal，emit() 与 connect()"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"要点：优先信号而非直接调用；零轮询，性能高"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"状态模式"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"实现：AnimationTree + 状态机；LimboAI 行为树"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"要点：动画与逻辑深度结合；行为树对复杂 AI 策划友好"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"三、游戏层架构实践","layout_fish-bone-master_offset":{"x":6,"y":-16}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"游戏流程管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"场景切换：SceneTree.change_scene_to_file"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"异步加载：ResourceLoader.load_interactive"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"全局服务：Autoload 单例（如 GameState, AudioManager）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"数据驱动与配置"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"自定义 Resource：为武器、角色创建可编辑数据资产"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"CSV / JSON 解析：传统表格方案"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"godot-google-sheet 插件：在线协作配置"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"存档系统"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"基础：Dictionary + FileAccess 写入 .cfg"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"进阶：自定义 Resource + ResourceSaver 保存 .tres/.res"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"对象池"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"时机：频繁生成/销毁（子弹、特效）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"结构：Node 管理器预实例化，激活/重置复用"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"四、UI 架构"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"MVC / MVVM 模式"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"分离：Model(数据), View(界面), Controller/ViewModel(逻辑)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"工具：gd-data-binding, Godot MVC 等插件"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"UI 栈管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"通过父节点控制子节点 visible 或 add_child/remove_child"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"实现界面压入、弹出生命期"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"五、底层系统与资源管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"资源管理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"机制：引用计数，同路径不重复加载"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"接口：load/preload，ResourceGroups 插件分包加载"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"渲染架构"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"RenderingServer：底层渲染 API 单例"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"Compositor：脚本化全屏后处理效果"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"定制与扩展"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"GDExtension (C++)：高性能原生代码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"C#/.NET：NuGet 包集成，.NET 8 支持"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"六、网络同步架构"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"推荐：权威服务器架构 (Headless Server)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"高层 API：MultiplayerSpawner / MultiplayerSynchronizer"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"模式选择：偏向状态同步；RTS 等可考虑帧同步（需确定性逻辑）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"通信：@rpc 注解远程过程调用"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"七、GDScript 架构实践建议"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"class_name：注册自定义类，增强代码提示"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"Resource 解耦：避免数据硬编码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"静态类型：指定类型提升性能和 IDE 检查"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"Groups：节点分组，批量操作 (get_tree().call_group)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"慎用 $ 路径：优先信号与依赖注入"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"八、实践项目与资源推荐"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"实践路径"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"入门：2D 平台/射击，串通角色、UI、计分、关卡切换"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"专项练习：状态机重写，事件总线，MVC 解耦属性与 UI"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"权威书籍"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"《Game Development Patterns with Godot 4》"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"《Essential Guide to Creating Multiplayer Games with Godot 4.0》"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"范例项目"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"Godot Tactical RPG (策略 RPG 分层设计)"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"Godot Performance C (C 高性能与 ECS 结合)"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"播客/视频：搜索 Godot Architecture, GDScript Best Practices"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"实用插件"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"godot-ecs (轻量 ECS)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"phantom-camera (灵活相机控制)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"dialogue-manager (叙事对话系统)"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"fish-bone","theme":"classic-compact","version":"1.4.43"}